                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14553547" author="tjwatson" created="Thu, 21 May 2015 02:55:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Possible fix is to return the internal copy of the candidates when adding them to Candidates so we can modify them correctly when inserting hosted capabilities for dynamic package resolution&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14554230" author="tjwatson" created="Thu, 21 May 2015 12:52:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Alternative fix.  This fix is likely better because it behaves more closely to the normal resolution flow where processCandidates is called before adding the candidate lists to the Candidates data structure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14554306" author="rickhall" created="Thu, 21 May 2015 13:58:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks simple enough, I&apos;ve applied. Please close if satisfied, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
